abstract: A three-bedroom duplex is on the 32nd and 33rd floors of Warren Street.
lead_paragraph: A three-bedroom TriBeCa penthouse with a 22-foot-high wraparound loggia offering open river and Midtown views that sold for $6.9 million was the most expensive transaction of the week, according to city records.
